high_descs: Turn to your right and go past the island and past the stove, to the kitchen sink ahead and to your left.
Pick up the butter knife in the sink, behind the egg and the coffee cup.
Turn to your right and go to the counter top to the left of the stove.
Cut the apple to the right of the bread, on the counter into slices.
Turn around and go to the sink on your right.
Place the knife in the left side of the sink.
Turn to your right and go back to the counter top with the apple on it, across from you.
Pick up one of the apple slices from the counter top.
Turn around and go to the sink on your right.
Place the apple slice in the sink, turn the water on, rinse off the apple slice, turn the water off, and remove the apple slice from the sink.
Turn to the refrigerator on your left.
Place the apple on the front, center of the top shelf of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the sink and a clean apple slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn right and walk forward to face the apple on the sink.
Cut the apple on the sink into three pieces.
Turn left to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn right to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up the apple piece on the counter.
Turn left to face the sink.
Wash the apple piece in the sink and then remove it.
Step to the left to face the fridge.
Place the apple piece in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To wash an apple piece and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: turn around, then move left around the center table until you get to the sink directly behind it
pick up the knife in the sink
go right, then straight to the counter top to the left of the stove top
slice the apple to the left of the stove top
return to facing the sink
place the knife to the left of the egg in the sink
return to the counter top section to the left of the stove
pick up a slice of apple from the counter top
return to the sink
place the apple in the sink, fill the sink with water and let the apple get wet before taking the apple slice out
face the refrigerator to the left of the sink
open the refrigerator and place the apple slice in front of the toast
anns.task_desc: slice the apple, rinse it off in the sink, and cool it in the refrigerator
